  "title": "Network Engineer (Ref 26324)",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities<br />• Perform network configuration, monitoring, and troubleshooting.<br />• Ensure network availability, performance, and security<br />• Support firewall, VPN, and network security operations<br />• Monitor and respond to network incidents and service outages<br />• Perform network upgrades, patching, and routine maintenance<br />• Maintain accurate network documentation and diagrams<br />• Work with vendors, service providers, and internal teams<br />• Participate in on-call or after-hours support when required<br /><br />Requirements<br />• Degree in Computer Science / IT or equivalent<br />• Minimum 3 years of experience in Network support and maintenance.<br />• Experience with Aruba networking products such as Aruba Clearpass Policy Manager.<br />• Experience with Check Point firewalls (policy management, VPN, security rules)<br />• Minimum CCNA Certified<br /></p><p>Licence no: 12C6060</p>",
